The paper focuses on face alignment using CNNs, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves joint optimization with different loss functions, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates the method on multiple datasets, which is common in multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) research.
